briefdescription.para: Runs the Classifier algorithm on incoming message flows.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This runs a priority based classification algorithm that pops messages from incoming message flows, and copies the messages to the priority queue specified in the configuration table.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: There is only one caller of this function and this caller enforces that the call will never contain a null pointer, therefore the null pointer condition is not checked.

parameterdescription.para: A TO_ChannelData_t pointer that references the channel data structure
